PART 4: THE DEEPER MODULAR LAW — WHEN DOES x² | (I-1)?
======================================================================

α₁ parity at n=3..6:
  n=3: α₁ mod 2 distribution: {0: 7, 1: 1}
  n=3: α₁ mod 3 distribution: {0: 7, 1: 1}
  n=3: α₁ mod 4 distribution: {0: 7, 1: 1}
