  n=4: α₁ mod 3 distribution: {0: 40, 1: 16, 2: 8}
  n=4: α₁ mod 4 distribution: {0: 40, 1: 16, 2: 8}
  n=4: α₁ mod 5 distribution: {0: 40, 1: 16, 2: 8}
  n=4: α₁ mod 6 distribution: {0: 40, 1: 16, 2: 8}
